com.microsoft.azure.management.sql

Class ServerAdministratorOperationsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.management.sql.ServerAdministratorOperationsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServerAdministratorOperations, ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>

    public class ServerAdministratorOperationsImpl
extends Object
implements ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>, ServerAdministratorOperations
    Represents all the operations for operating on Azure SQL Server Active Directory Administrators. Contains operations to: Create, Retrieve, Update, and Delete Azure SQL Server Active Directory Administrators.
